Depends: bash, coreutils, grep, sed, awk, lxc-pve | pve-container, pve-manager, curl, screen, util-linux
Description: Tools to create and manage Minecraft servers on Proxmox LXC
Bridge networking only, no RCON, autostart always, daily backups via cron.
Includes mc setup, mc clone (auto-detect Java/Bedrock), and management commands.
